### HelloAsso v5 API — playground
### Doc: https://api.helloasso.com/v5/swagger/index.html
### Variables: http-client.env.json (public) + http-client.private.env.json (secrets, gitignoré)

### --- 1. OAuth token (client_credentials) ---
# @name auth
POST {{baseUrl}}/oauth2/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

client_id={{clientId}}&client_secret={{clientSecret}}&grant_type=client_credentials

> {%
client.global.set("token", response.body.access_token);
%}

### --- 2. Form public model : définitions des questions custom ---
### Les questions = tiers[].customFields[] (label, type, isRequired, values pour ChoiceList)
###                  + extraOptions[].customFields[]
GET {{baseUrl}}/v5/organizations/{{orgSlug}}/forms/{{formType}}/{{formSlug}}/public
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### --- 3. Items du formulaire AVEC réponses customFields ---
### withDetails=true OBLIGATOIRE sinon customFields absent de la réponse
### Réponses dans items[].customFields[] = {id, name, type, answer}
GET {{baseUrl}}/v5/organizations/{{orgSlug}}/forms/{{formType}}/{{formSlug}}/items
    ?withDetails=true
    &pageSize=100
    &pageIndex=1
